<subSubSection id="0FC96579FFE389677DCDA2B2B87CFCC8" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="476C36F2FFE389677DCDA2B2B87CFCC8" blockId="53.[151,1436,151,255]" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis id="75A7EAE0FFE389677DCDA2B2BB63FC86" bold="true" box="[199,320,151,177]" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Remarks.</emphasis>
Members of 
<taxonomicName id="80D34D71FFE389677CEEA2BDB87CFC86" box="[484,607,152,177]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Platyledra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="75A7EAE0FFE389677CEEA2BDB87CFC86" box="[484,607,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Platyledra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are defined by their acuminate crowns and dorsoventrally depressed pronota bearing a single medial longitudinal crest. They form a monophyletic group (the 
<taxonomicName id="80D34D71FFE3896779D5A29ABF6FFCEF" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1907" box="[1247,1356,191,216]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Jukaruka" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="75A7EAE0FFE3896779D5A29ABF6FFCEF" box="[1247,1356,191,216]" italics="true" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Jukaruka</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
genus group) with 
<taxonomicName id="80D34D71FFE389677C22A2C0BBB6FCC9" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1907" box="[296,405,229,254]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Jukaruka" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="75A7EAE0FFE389677C22A2C0BBB6FCC9" box="[296,405,229,254]" italics="true" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Jukaruka</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="80D34D71FFE389677CC7A2C0B87BFCC9" baseAuthorityName="Fletcher" baseAuthorityYear="2006" box="[461,600,229,254]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Ledropsella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
